  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3575940/extras/477d0814d1afe132c889a91adf5607e6.avif?t=1743027241\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3575940/extras_big/477d0814d1afe132c889a91adf5607e6.avif?t=1743027241 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Command the Skies in a High-Octane Steampunk Bullet Hell!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take control of a powerful steampunk airship and soar into battle across stunning hand-drawn skies. <br><br><strong>Dodge waves of bullets</strong>, unleash devastating firepower, and prove your skill in this fast-paced, action-packed bullet hell shooter!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3575940/extras/0e418c9a06686a7ca84a25f6098716d0.poster.avif?t=1743027241\" width=608 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3575940/extras/0e418c9a06686a7ca84a25f6098716d0.webm?t=1743027241\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3575940/extras/0e418c9a06686a7ca84a25f6098716d0.mp4?t=1743027241\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🌍 <strong>Blast Through Three Distinct Worlds</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Journey through beautifully crafted steampunk-inspired landscapes, each teeming with relentless enemies and intricate bullet patterns. Each world consisting new dangers and foes. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3575940/extras/ab2d1a87e4f424a1813864427f4b2afa.poster.avif?t=1743027241\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3575940/extras/ab2d1a87e4f424a1813864427f4b2afa.webm?t=1743027241\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3575940/extras/ab2d1a87e4f424a1813864427f4b2afa.mp4?t=1743027241\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face off against <strong>three unique and formidable bosses</strong>, each more intense than the last. Can you survive the storm?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3575940/extras/9412948a405afd1153de0bd180db14ff.poster.avif?t=1743027241\" width=608 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3575940/extras/9412948a405afd1153de0bd180db14ff.webm?t=1743027241\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3575940/extras/9412948a405afd1153de0bd180db14ff.mp4?t=1743027241\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🔧 <strong>Upgrade. Customize. Dominate.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect loot to upgrade your ship’s stats and arsenal.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Visit the <strong>Hangar</strong> to enhance your Health, Armor, and Energy—fuel for your powerful secondary weapons.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Drop by the <strong>Weapons Shop</strong> to unlock a wide variety of primary and secondary weapons that suit your playstyle and tactics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3575940/extras/5fa4bfb57f510f6dcec241e1acea8633.poster.avif?t=1743027241\" width=608 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3575940/extras/5fa4bfb57f510f6dcec241e1acea8633.webm?t=1743027241\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3575940/extras/5fa4bfb57f510f6dcec241e1acea8633.mp4?t=1743027241\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🎯 <strong>Choose Your Challenge</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Adjust the difficulty to match your pace—from laid-back sky explorer to hardcore bullet-dodging ace.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether you're here for the adventure or the adrenaline, the skies hold your destiny.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >⚔️ Do you have what it takes to conquer all three bosses and become the <strong>Ultimate Captain of the Skies</strong>?</h2>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3575940/extras/477d0814d1afe132c889a91adf5607e6.avif?t=1743027241\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3575940/extras_big/477d0814d1afe132c889a91adf5607e6.avif?t=1743027241 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Command the Skies in a High-Octane Steampunk Bullet Hell!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take control of a powerful steampunk airship and soar into battle across stunning hand-drawn skies. <br><br><strong>Dodge waves of bullets</strong>, unleash devastating firepower, and prove your skill in this fast-paced, action-packed bullet hell shooter!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3575940/extras/0e418c9a06686a7ca84a25f6098716d0.poster.avif?t=1743027241\" width=608 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3575940/extras/0e418c9a06686a7ca84a25f6098716d0.webm?t=1743027241\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3575940/extras/0e418c9a06686a7ca84a25f6098716d0.mp4?t=1743027241\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🌍 <strong>Blast Through Three Distinct Worlds</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Journey through beautifully crafted steampunk-inspired landscapes, each teeming with relentless enemies and intricate bullet patterns. Each world consisting new dangers and foes. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3575940/extras/ab2d1a87e4f424a1813864427f4b2afa.poster.avif?t=1743027241\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3575940/extras/ab2d1a87e4f424a1813864427f4b2afa.webm?t=1743027241\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3575940/extras/ab2d1a87e4f424a1813864427f4b2afa.mp4?t=1743027241\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face off against <strong>three unique and formidable bosses</strong>, each more intense than the last. Can you survive the storm?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3575940/extras/9412948a405afd1153de0bd180db14ff.poster.avif?t=1743027241\" width=608 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3575940/extras/9412948a405afd1153de0bd180db14ff.webm?t=1743027241\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3575940/extras/9412948a405afd1153de0bd180db14ff.mp4?t=1743027241\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🔧 <strong>Upgrade. Customize. Dominate.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect loot to upgrade your ship’s stats and arsenal.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Visit the <strong>Hangar</strong> to enhance your Health, Armor, and Energy—fuel for your powerful secondary weapons.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Drop by the <strong>Weapons Shop</strong> to unlock a wide variety of primary and secondary weapons that suit your playstyle and tactics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3575940/extras/5fa4bfb57f510f6dcec241e1acea8633.poster.avif?t=1743027241\" width=608 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3575940/extras/5fa4bfb57f510f6dcec241e1acea8633.webm?t=1743027241\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3575940/extras/5fa4bfb57f510f6dcec241e1acea8633.mp4?t=1743027241\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🎯 <strong>Choose Your Challenge</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Adjust the difficulty to match your pace—from laid-back sky explorer to hardcore bullet-dodging ace.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether you're here for the adventure or the adrenaline, the skies hold your destiny.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >⚔️ Do you have what it takes to conquer all three bosses and become the <strong>Ultimate Captain of the Skies</strong>?</h2>",
